\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 In the context of an insurance company\'92s provider network, 
\f1\b delegations
\f0\b0  refer to the transfer of certain operational responsibilities from the health plan (payer) to another entity\'97typically a 
\f1\b provider organization, medical group, IPA (Independent Practice Association), or vendor
\f0\b0 \'97while the insurer 
\f1\b retains ultimate accountability
\f0\b0 .\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
