\pard\pardeftab720\sa348\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs42 \cf0 \strokec2 \uc0\u55358 \u56809  What Delegation Means (Simple Definition)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs28 \cf0 A 
\f1\b delegation
\f0\b0  is when an insurance company allows a provider organization (or third party) to perform specific functions on its behalf, rather than the insurer doing them centrally.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa348\partightenfactor0

